- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the height of languages, which is a fundamental concept in formal language theory. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper discusses the complexity of the logic of subwords. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper develops new techniques for bounding the height of languages. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper deals with descriptive complexity measures. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper discusses the complexity of the logic of subwords.
